  description: "concurrent.futures ThreadPoolExecutor absent instance attrs and ProcessPoolExecutor membership in cfextra83 namespace — wave 246 theme: concurrent.futures ThreadPoolExecutor.__dict__ membership; ThreadPoolExecutor.__dict__.__contains__('_initializer')==False (instance attr set in __init__, not a class-level entry); ThreadPoolExecutor.__dict__.__contains__('_work_queue')==False (instance attr set in __init__); ProcessPoolExecutor.__dict__.__contains__('submit')==True; ProcessPoolExecutor.__dict__.__contains__('shutdown')==True; verified with Python 3.14.3"
